    • query

      public org.apache.jena.query.QueryExecution query(String queryString)
      Description copied from interface: RDFConnection
      Setup a SPARQL query execution. This is a low-level operation. Handling the QueryExecution should be done with try-resource. Some QueryExecutions, such as ones connecting to a remote server, need to be properly closed to release system resources. See also RDFConnection.querySelect(String, Consumer), RDFConnection.queryConstruct(String), RDFConnection.queryDescribe(String), RDFConnection.queryAsk(String) for ways to execute queries of a specific form.
      Specified by:
